Some re-usable automator actions.

###git-create-server-repo

Creates a new git repo ready for server use. Drop a folder onto the app where you want the repo created.

It initializes the repo with git like this:

git init --bare
git update-server-info

###make-icons-from-1024-1024

Makes a bunch of resized pngs from a 1024x1024 image.
